CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 2, 1957, pg. B6, reads: "WAILING WAILERS CLUB ANNIVERSARY - The Wailing Wailers Club, composed of several charming young ladies of the Beltzhoover area, celebrated its third anniversary, Oct. 26, at the residence of Sandra Cole. The club members are, left to right: Gwendolyn Martin, Dawsolene Plummer, Sonia Marton, Letricia Plummer, Carol Wilson, Patricia Robinson, president; Nancy Martin, Bertha Hall, Brenda Sells, Janie Boyce and Sandra Cole. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Wailing Wailers Club members including Gwendolyn Martin, Dawsolene Plummer, Sonia Marton, Letricia Plummer, Carol Wilson, president Patricia Robinson holding sheet cake inscribed "Happy Anniversary Wailing Wailers," Nancy Martin, Bertha Hall, Brenda Sells, Janie Boyce and Sandra Cole, gathered behind rose patterned tablecloth, in home of Sandra Cole
